'''Kindrift''' (aka '''Raix Digital Epic''', '''Raiya Daimonion''', '''Railfoxen'''. '''Icevixen''', '''Downspin''') is a mentally ill furry from Buttcrack, Nevada; who believes [[schizophrenic|coyotes talk to him]] and who has a keen interest in the [[pedo|babyfur]] scene.  But of course, calling a furry mentally ill is redundant.

Formerly a [[moot|mod]] at [[CrushYiffDestroy]], Kindrift was eventually banned by [[Chris Chan|fat old pedo]] Mitch the Bitch for aggravated faggotry. He then set off in a hissy fit to set up his own site, the astoundingly limp-dicked [[CrushYiffDestroy#CYD_Jr.|Vivisector]] where he could freely [[masturbate|indulge]] his [[rapist|perverse]] obsession with [[Xydexx]] and other far less savory topics.

Drifty is currently setting up a business to sell animal shaped dildos, all personally inspected and verified to work.



